# profileLabel

**Instance Property**

The name to assign to the profile.

## Declaration

```swift
var profileLabel: String? { get }
```

## Discussion

Use this property if your vehicle supports saving named profiles.

## Getting the Profile Information

- **profileNumber**: The profile index in which to save the settings.
- **profileName**: The name to assign to the profile.
